==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ungrave
<hw>Un*grave"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>grave</ets>.]</ety> <def>To raise or remove from
the grave; to disinter; to untomb; to exhume.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Fuller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

